- Track changes: View audit trails for user actions
- Identify issues: Detect unusual patterns or errors
- Support users: Assist with access and permission issues

System maintenance:
- Database migrations: Run Alembic migrations for schema updates
- Backup operations: Coordinate database backups and restores
- Performance monitoring: Review query performance and indexes
- Log analysis: Review application logs for errors and warnings

Requires permission: All permissions (administrator role)', 'administrator', true, '2026-01-10 19:32:31.030314', NULL, '2026-01-10 19:32:31.030314', NULL);
INSERT INTO public.help_entries VALUES ('de9c54cd-a58c-4511-b955-b64a3beb9ef1', 'Getting Started', 'Welcome to NimbleLIMS! As an Administrator, you manage the entire system:

